---

<html lang="sv">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<title>QR Preview — vmtipset</title>
		<style>
			@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');

			body {
				font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
				background: #0a0e14;
				color: #f0f0f0;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 3rem 2rem;
			}

			h1 {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
				color: #fecc02;
			}

			.grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
				gap: 2rem;
				max-width: 1100px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}

			.card {
				background: #111825;
				padding: 2rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				text-align: center;
			}

			.card h2 {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				font-size: 1.3rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.card p {
				color: #8a9ab5;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}

			.qr-wrap {
				background: #fff;
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 1rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
			}

			.qr-wrap img {
				display: block;
				width: 250px;
				height: 250px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>Välj QR-stil</h1>
		<div class="grid">
			<div class="card">
				<h2>1. Celeste</h2>
				<p>Rundade prickar i celeste/teal. Clean och elegant.</p>
				<div class="qr-wrap">
					<img src="/qr-celeste.svg" alt="Celeste QR" />
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h2>2. Gradient</h2>
				<p>Blå-celeste gradient med gula hörn. Sverige × Uruguay.</p>
				<div class="qr-wrap">
					<img src="/qr-gradient.svg" alt="Gradient QR" />
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h2>3. Classic</h2>
				<p>Mörkblå rundade prickar. Minimalt men polerat.</p>
				<div class="qr-wrap">
					<img src="/qr-classic.svg" alt="Classic QR" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
